additional_info.title: FAQ 1
additional_info.body:
Q: I control Cogsworth- Grandfather Clock and his Unwind ability is giving all of my other characters Resist +1. If I play a Mother Gothel- Withered and Wicked, how much damage will be on her?

A: 3 damage. Mother Gothelâ€™s ability does not count as damaging her so even if she has Resist she will still enter play with 3 damage counters on her.

flavor_text: Her feelings are written all over her face.
rules_text: WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?! This character enters play with 3 damage.
